_sText: This is a retexture and edit of gg_pink_panther_2 created by mck-76. I got tired of my favorite map emptying my clans gungame server just because it was pink, so I decided to retexture it. I ended up not only replacing the textures, but doing major edits to the lighting and making a couple of structural changes. Non-Texture Based Changes From Original Pink Panther include ladders to access the top, torches in the underground areas for lighting, and some minor structural changes for visual improvement. The torch prefab I made for this project can be found here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/3803 This map can be found on the mfcgaming.net Reverse Gungame5 Elimination Server @ 69.39.229.49:27015 The rar file contains the map and nav files as well as bzip version of both for fastdl servers. Please play the map, rate and comment. Thanks!
